cs.GR, cs.CV, cs.CG, cs.MM, cs.AI. 

The paper deals with the problem of synthesizing pebble mosaics from images, which involves both image processing and computer graphics techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.GR (Computer Graphics), followed by cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.CG (Computational Geometry). The paper also uses clustering algorithms and solves a Laplace equation, which are techniques commonly used in machine learning and artificial intelligence, hence cs.MM (Multimedia) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) are also possible categories.
